text:
My account has been banned for over two months now, and I’ve sent many emails to Telegram Help, yet I haven’t received any response back. It’s honestly frustrating especially that I haven’t done anything that violates Telegram rules. So I hope this review will get me a response from the Telegram team.

Disclaimer: I only rated this 5 stars so it can be shown at the top.
